Happy Father’s Day, Dad!

Happy Father’s Day to all the dads out there!!

Traditionally, on Father’s Day we should cook a meaty dish for Dad. I was busy over the weekend so we only had this meal this week. We had about 300 grams of sirloin steak. I cut standard slices of about 6 to 8 mm. The marinade was soy sauce, a small amount of salt, olive oil, tomato sauce and black pepper. It was not over-the-top-long-marinated, though. Just for a few minutes.
